Hi Jennifer,

You say that you book has 
  
   x^2 + 2x remainder 46?

Are you sure didn't mean

   x^2 + 2x -12 remainder 46?

In any case, I think if you'll be a little more careful with you 
subtraction you'll see what the problem is.

